reviewText: Save your money.  This dvd is boring, poor quality film.  Unless you competed at this event or know someone who did you'll probably want to skip this.
I love these dvds seeing the holds and the techniques in action , I  heard about grapplers quest online but never seen it til i got the dvds and will be buying more in the near future.
I've watched and helped produce 6 Grappling Titles to date and this is by far, my favorite to date.  The competition level is AMAZING.  The American Grapplers are some of the BEST on the planet.
